OL,6,FWords by Production Journalist Michael
OL,7,FJones
OL,9,FThe latest release of the Epstein
OL,10,Ffiles has had a big impact in the UK,
OL,11,Fwith the arrest of a former prince and
OL,12,Fa Lord.
OL,14,FBut as well as the high-profile cases
OL,15,Fof Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor and Lord
OL,16,FPeter Mandelson, which have
OL,17,Freverberated through British politics,
OL,18,Fthe shockwaves have been felt around
OL,19,Fthe world.
