OL,3,CWho else has faced fallout from the
OL,4,CEpstein files?
OL,6,FAlthough being mentioned in the files
OL,7,Fis no indication of wrongdoing, some
OL,8,Fprominent figures who appear in the
OL,9,Ffiles have resigned, lost their jobs,
OL,10,For been placed under investigation.
OL,12,FSo who else has been impacted by the
OL,13,FEpstein files, and how have they
OL,14,Fresponded? ITV News explains.
OL,16,FFormer Norwegian Prime Minister,
OL,17,FThorbjorn Jagland - Criminally charged
