OL,3,CWho else has faced fallout from the
OL,4,CEpstein files?
OL,6,FJagland, a former prime minister of
OL,7,FNorway, was charged with "aggravated
OL,8,Fcorruption" in connection with his
OL,9,Fties to convicted paedophile Jeffrey
OL,10,FEpstein on February 12, according to
OL,11,FNorwegian police.
OL,13,FThe Norwegian National Authority for
OL,14,FInvestigation and Prosecution of
OL,15,FEconomic and Environmental Crime said
OL,16,Fit is investigating whether gifts,
OL,17,Ftravel, and loans were received in
OL,18,Fconnection with Jagland's position.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
