OL,6,FHe served as Norway's prime minister
OL,7,Fbetween 1996 and 1997 before a 10-year
OL,8,Fstint as the secretary general of the
OL,9,FCouncil of Europe (2009-2019).
OL,11,FThe Council of Europe's Committee of
OL,12,FMinisters waived its immunity of
OL,13,FJagland to allow criminal proceedings
OL,14,Fto take place.
OL,16,FHis lawyer says Jagland denies
OL,17,Fcriminal liability and is willing to
OL,18,Fcooperate.
