OL,3,CWho else has faced fallout from the
OL,4,CEpstein files?
OL,6,FPritzker stepped down as executive
OL,7,Fchairman of the Hyatt Hotels
OL,8,FCorporation on February 16, following
OL,9,Fyears of communication between him and
OL,10,FEpstein, after the latter was
OL,11,Fconvicted in 2008.
OL,13,FPritzker says he exercised "terrible
OL,14,Fjudgment" in maintaining contact with
OL,15,FEpstein and Ghislaine Maxwell.
OL,17,FThe multinational hotel company owns
OL,18,Fhotels across the world, including the
OL,19,Ffive-star Great Eastern Hotel in
OL,20,Fcentral London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
