OL,14,FSulayem was the head of global ports
OL,15,Foperator DP World, but the company
OL,16,Fannounced his resignation as
OL,17,F"effective immediately" on February 13
OL,18,Fafter files showed hundreds of emails
OL,19,Fbetween the Emirati businessman and
OL,20,FEpstein.
