OL,6,FThe emails included messages from
OL,7,FSulayem describing women, one of which
OL,8,Fincluded details about their age,
OL,9,Fweight, height, and bra size.
OL,11,FEpstein described Sulayem as "one of
OL,12,Fhis most trusted friends" in an email
OL,13,Ffrom June 2013.
