OL,3,CWho else has faced fallout from the
OL,4,CEpstein files?
OL,6,FThe American head of the 2028 Los
OL,7,FAngeles Games (LA28) has revealed he
OL,8,Fis selling his agency, The Wasserman
OL,9,FGroup.
OL,11,FWasserman has not been accused of any
OL,12,Fwrongdoing in connection with Epstein,
OL,13,Fbut documents released by the DOJ
OL,14,Frevealed that in 2003, he exchanged
OL,15,Fflirtatious emails with Maxwell, who,
OL,16,Fyears later, was sentenced to 20 years
OL,17,Fin prison for conspiring with the
OL,18,Fconvicted paedophile to sexually abuse
OL,19,Fminors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
