OL,3,CWho else has faced fallout from the
OL,4,CEpstein files?
OL,6,FLA28 said Wasserman would remain
OL,7,Fchairman of the 2028 games after
OL,8,Forganisers reviewed his past
OL,9,Finteractions with Maxwell.
OL,11,FThey found his relationship did not go
OL,12,Ffurther than the exchanges that had
OL,13,Falready been documented and that he
OL,14,Fhad fully cooperated with an
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,FHowever, he did step down from his
OL,18,Fagency after Pink Pony Club singer
OL,19,FChappell Roan left in protest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
