OL,6,FThe 27-year-old Grammy winner said on
OL,7,FInstagram: "No artist, agent or
OL,8,Femployee should ever be expected to
OL,9,Fdefend or overlook actions that
OL,10,Fconflict so deeply with our own moral
OL,11,Fvalues."
OL,13,FWasserman said in his memo to staff
OL,14,Fthat his interactions with Maxwell and
OL,15,FEpstein were limited and that he
OL,16,Fregrets the emails.
