OL,6,FThe former Norwegian ambassador to the
OL,7,FUK (2014-2019), Juul, stepped down as
OL,8,FNorway's ambassador to Jordan and Iraq
OL,9,Fon February 8 after revelations about
OL,10,Fher and her husband's financial
OL,11,Fdealings with Epstein.
OL,13,FReports in Norway alleged Juul had a
OL,14,Fwill signed by Epstein days before he
OL,15,Fdied, granting each of her children
OL,16,F#3.6 million in a will.
OL,18,FHer lawyer has denied the allegations.
