OL,3,CWho else has faced fallout from the
OL,4,CEpstein files?
OL,6,FThe fifth president of the Maldives
OL,7,F(2012-2013) departed his latest post
OL,8,Fas Special Envoy of the President at
OL,9,Fthe beginning of the month (February
OL,10,F3) after the latest files showed him
OL,11,Fseeking financial guidance from
OL,12,FEpstein numerous times between 2012
OL,13,Fand 2015.
OL,15,FAccording to reports in the Maldives,
OL,16,FWaheed viewed Epstein as a trusted
OL,17,Fadvisor. Previously disclosed emails
OL,18,Falso show the former president
OL,19,Fattempting to work with Epstein to
OL,20,Fdevelop a private island in the
OL,21,FMaldives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
