OL,6,FWaheed has told ITV News that he was
OL,7,Frecommended Epstein's advice on a
OL,8,Fnumber of financial and professional
OL,9,Fissues during his presidency.
OL,11,FAfter his tenure in office, Waheed
OL,12,Fadmitted to approaching Epstein for
OL,13,Finvestment in the Maldives for islands
OL,14,Fheld by the politician's friends. He
OL,15,Fstressed that Epstein never came
OL,16,Fthrough with these investments.
