OL,6,FThe university said it had decided to
OL,7,Fremove the name and bust of its former
OL,8,FChancellor, Senator George J.
OL,9,FMitchell, from the Institute for
OL,10,FGlobal Peace, Security and Justice.
OL,12,FIt stated: "While no findings of
OL,13,Fwrongdoing by Senator Mitchell have
OL,14,Fbeen made, the university has
OL,15,Fconcluded that, in light of this
OL,16,Fmaterial, and mindful of the
OL,17,Fexperiences of victims and survivors,
OL,18,Fit is no longer appropriate for its
OL,19,Finstitutional spaces and entities to
OL,20,Fcontinue to bear his name."
